messages.msg: Welcome to our site! If you are looking for prayer or someone to chat with, reply to this message or email us at prayer@fightlust.com
I want to renounce the sins of fornication adultery harlotry masturbation lust homosexuality and pornography

We can certainly support you in this. Here’s a prayer you can use to renounce those sins:

"Heavenly Father, I come before you today to renounce all sexual sins that I have been involved in, including fornication, adultery, harlotry, masturbation, lust, homosexuality, and pornography. In the name of Jesus Christ, I break all curses associated with these sins and ask for your forgiveness and cleansing. I present my body to you as a living sacrifice and seek your strength to walk in purity. Amen."

If you need further guidance or support, feel free to ask!
I repent for allowing these sins to become an idol in my life and I pray that I would stop practicing these sins I ask for deliverance from these evil spirits

It's great to hear your desire for repentance and deliverance. Here’s a prayer you can use:

"Heavenly Father, I repent for allowing these sins to become an idol in my life. I ask for your forgiveness and for the strength to stop practicing these sins. In the name of Jesus Christ, I pray for deliverance from all evil spirits associated with fornication, adultery, harlotry, masturbation, lust, homosexuality, and pornography. I ask that you cleanse me and fill me with your Holy Spirit to walk in purity. Amen."

If you need more support or resources, just let me know!
I renounce blasphemy self righteousness narcissism and I ask that the holy spirit would release me from these sins and fill me afresh to walk in true Godliness and holiness

That's a powerful prayer of renunciation. Here’s a prayer you can use:

"Heavenly Father, I renounce blasphemy, self-righteousness, and narcissism. I ask that the Holy Spirit would release me from these sins and fill me afresh. Help me to walk in true godliness and holiness. I seek your strength and guidance to live a life that honors you. Amen."

If you need further assistance or resources, feel free to reach out!
I ask God to lead me out of all falsehood lies deception error sexual sins and to lead me into a true relationship with him where I'm living a life of truth sexual integrity and holiness

That's a beautiful prayer for guidance and integrity. Here’s a prayer you can use:

"Heavenly Father, I ask you to lead me out of all falsehood, lies, deception, error, and sexual sins. Guide me into a true relationship with you, where I can live a life of truth, sexual integrity, and holiness. Help me to seek you earnestly and to walk in your ways. Amen."

If you need more support or resources, I'm here to help!

I renounce and repent of the ways I have used my body as an instrument of unrighteousness I pray against all strongholds of sexual immorality and deception I release myself from all opposing thoughts words and deeds that goes against holiness truth and righteousness I pray that I would be faithful to God so I can in return be a faithful husband

That's a heartfelt prayer of renunciation and commitment. Here’s a prayer you can use:

"Heavenly Father, I renounce and repent of the ways I have used my body as an instrument of unrighteousness. I pray against all strongholds of sexual immorality and deception. I release myself from all opposing thoughts, words, and deeds that go against holiness, truth, and righteousness. I ask for your strength to be faithful to you, so I can be a faithful husband. Fill me with your Spirit and guide me in your ways. Amen."

If you need further support or resources, just let me know!

I renounce and repent of all sins of idolatry all sinful practices especially sexual immorality I ask for spiritual eyes to see things with the spiritual eyes I ask God to release me from the will of satan and for him to lead me into all truth as and obedient servant I repent for not allowing him to lead me and for walking in rebellion and practicing witchcraft which is rebellion

That's a sincere prayer of renunciation and repentance. Here’s a prayer you can use:

"Heavenly Father, I renounce and repent of all sins of idolatry and all sinful practices, especially sexual immorality. I ask for spiritual eyes to see things as you see them. Please release me from the will of Satan and lead me into all truth as your obedient servant. I repent for not allowing you to lead me and for walking in rebellion and practicing witchcraft, which is rebellion against you. Fill me with your Spirit and guide me in your ways. Amen."

If you need more support or resources, I'm here to help!
I especially renounce repent and ask forgiveness for the sin of adultery I ask for deliverance and cleansing from all unclean spirits that leads to adultery

That's a powerful prayer of renunciation and seeking forgiveness. Here’s a prayer you can use:

"Heavenly Father, I especially renounce, repent, and ask for forgiveness for the sin of adultery. I ask for deliverance and cleansing from all unclean spirits that lead to adultery. Please purify my heart and mind, and help me to walk in your ways. Fill me with your Spirit and guide me towards a life of purity and faithfulness. Amen."

If you need further assistance or resources, feel free to ask!

I ask God to release me from anything demonic that separates me from him lies deception sexual sins pride worldliness I pray for a willingness to be led by the spirit and not satan or the flesh I repent for all the ways I have grieved God and the holy spirit through sexual sin and rebellion and seeking my own direction in life following satan and the flesh

That's a heartfelt prayer of repentance and seeking deliverance. Here’s a prayer you can use:

"Heavenly Father, I ask you to release me from anything demonic that separates me from you—lies, deception, sexual sins, pride, and worldliness. I pray for a willingness to be led by your Spirit and not by Satan or the flesh. I repent for all the ways I have grieved you and the Holy Spirit through sexual sin and rebellion, and for seeking my own direction in life by following Satan and the flesh. Please cleanse me and guide me in your truth. Amen."

If you need more support or resources, I'm here to help!

I seek your will and direction for my life I renounce and repent of sins that would cause me to not fulfill my destiny especially sexual sins please empower me by your spirit to stop abusing and misusing your temple and body with sexual sin

That's a sincere prayer for guidance and empowerment. Here’s a prayer you can use:

"Heavenly Father, I seek your will and direction for my life. I renounce and repent of all sins that would cause me to not fulfill my destiny, especially sexual sins. Please empower me by your Spirit to stop abusing and misusing your temple and body with sexual sin. Help me to honor you in all that I do and to walk in your ways. Amen."

If you need further assistance or resources, feel free to reach out!

I pray for renewed sexual integrity that is pure and holy cleanse my sexuality with the blood of Christ and make my thoughts your thoughts create in me a clean heart and renew a right spirit within me destroy the altar of sexual immorality in my life

That's a powerful prayer for renewal and cleansing. Here’s a prayer you can use:

"Heavenly Father, I pray for renewed sexual integrity that is pure and holy. Cleanse my sexuality with the blood of Christ and make my thoughts your thoughts. Create in me a clean heart and renew a right spirit within me. Destroy the altar of sexual immorality in my life and help me to walk in purity and righteousness. Amen."

If you need more support or resources, I'm here to help!
Give me the direction I seek for my life remove satan from the throne in my life and take back your rightful position in my life I renounce idolatry in all forms

That's a heartfelt prayer for direction and surrender. Here’s a prayer you can use:

"Heavenly Father, I ask for the direction I seek for my life. Remove Satan from the throne in my life and take back your rightful position. I renounce idolatry in all forms and commit to serving you alone. Help me to follow your guidance and to live according to your will. Amen."

If you need further assistance or resources, feel free to reach out!
Not my will not the enemy will but let your will be done change me from the inside out that you maybe glorified bring me out spiritual darkness into your marvelous light

That's a beautiful prayer for transformation and guidance. Here’s a prayer you can use:

"Heavenly Father, not my will, nor the enemy's will, but let your will be done in my life. Change me from the inside out so that you may be glorified. Bring me out of spiritual darkness into your marvelous light. Help me to reflect your love and truth in all that I do. Amen."

If you need more support or resources, I'm here to help!
Let my trips to church bring about life transformation for the glory and honor of God let every trip to church draw me further away from sin and closer and closer to you

That's a wonderful prayer for transformation through your church visits. Here’s a prayer you can use:

"Heavenly Father, let my trips to church bring about life transformation for your glory and honor. May every visit draw me further away from sin and closer to you. Help me to grow in faith and to be strengthened in my walk with you. Amen."

If you need further assistance or resources, feel free to reach out!
